{"tid":1908004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[最大贏家] 羅致光稱未能向每名公務員提供口罩　員工購買後可報銷","createTime":"2020-03-03T03:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T04:16:54.000Z","uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2858bb56c86e563aed3feb2a92bc65f3269670","tid":1908004,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"政府部門昨日起陸續恢復公共服務，勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，勞福局本身沒太多直接面對公眾的服務，局方大部份員工仍然能夠居家工作，但轄下部份部門，例如社會福利署則有較多人需要返回辦公室工作，某些部門則採取彈性上班時間。他承認，不是所有部門都能夠向每名公務員提供口罩，但員工可自行為部門購買口罩，然後向政府報銷，限額為5萬元，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他透露有部門合共購買了20多萬元口罩</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光出席一個電台節目時說，估計失業率起碼會升至4%至5%，但難以估計會否高於2003年沙士時期的8.7%。他說，2003年之前沒自由行，以本地消費為主，但自去年年中至今，每日失去10多萬訪港遊客，令飲食、零售等行業大受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bb92e6c15d15ba2c83b7d1e4b2af30c7fd4d96","tid":1908004,"uid":187957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭又話唔洗帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ceb082516c27207c857c42af2dadb3369bc67e","tid":1908004,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"公墓員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n弓喜曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423eecd49a19de6a502826e22169089623953dd8","tid":1908004,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"公務員用公帑食炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n口罩價格應該可以再升一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2435573bd2d145d2d29